        private INIFileString m_RandomAttrSelected
        Size of the feature set used during tree induction. Used for random forests, random subspaces and bagging of subspaces. If left to default 0, floor(log_2 #DescAttr) + 1 is used.

        public java.util.List<java.lang.String> validateSettingsInternal()
        Description copied from class: SettingsBase
        This method should be overriden to check for inconsistencies in the section settings. It is called by si.ijs.kt.clus.main.settings.Settings.validateSettingsCompatibility() method.
